&lt;h3&gt;About the Author&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ruchir Sharma&lt;/strong&gt; penned the international bestseller &lt;em&gt;Breakout Nations&lt;/em&gt; and is a contributing op-ed writer at the &lt;em&gt;New York Times&lt;/em&gt;. His commentary has also appeared in the &lt;em&gt;Wall Street Journal&lt;/em&gt; , the &lt;em&gt;Financial Times&lt;/em&gt; , &lt;em&gt;Foreign Affairs&lt;/em&gt; , and other publications. He is chief global strategist at Morgan Stanley Investment Management, based in New York. --This text refers to the paperback edition.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</dc:description>
